tweet: Agenda?  When you are dealing with a big life moment, most of the convos revolve around that.   I spent a full year processing my divorce and feelings around it.   Right now I let the convo happen more organically with no set agenda.

tweet: Trauma does not = accusations   The word trauma has a negative connotation or that your parents were ‚Äúbad‚Äù.   It shouldn‚Äôt. It doesn‚Äôt.  On the surface I had a good childhood and going to therapy does not negate my parents‚Äô love for me.   We all have trauma.

name: Amanda Goetz
